{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8765eba1f9","title":"中央关于基本同意西北军区甘青指挥部的布告的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8269437542","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"8765eba1f9"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"843a8e41bd","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"经西北局补充修改后的布告第三条，原文是：“一切因受骗或被迫为的部落头人，僧俗群众，只要然归来，各安生产，一律既往不答，并保障其生命财产及以往之地位。”"},{"id":"b374af28d7","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"经西北局补充修改后的布告第五条，原文是：“无论汇首众，凡向人民政府及人民解放军投诚自新者，一律从宽处理；凡脱离汇众，并积极协助期汇者，允许将功折罪；对坚决为到底者，则坚决消灭之。"}],"contents":[{"id":"553f0c1ca7","type":"title","text":"中央关于基本同意西北军区甘青剩菲指挥部的布告的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9"},{"id":"843a8e41bd","type":"paragraph","text":"西北局，西北军区政治部，并转甘、青省委，并告西南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9"},{"id":"b374af28d7","type":"paragraph","text":"基本上同意西北局五月二日修改补充后的甘青期指布告。只是（一）第三条叫“嘴然归来”，改为“诚意回来”，较为通俗易懂：（二）第五条巴最后一句：“对坚决为到底者则坚决消灭之”，应册去，不绝首自新之路。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9"},{"id":"865e36685e","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9"},{"id":"6033f8b35d","type":"paragraph","text":"五月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9"}],"page":{"id":"20c5fe3138","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"8765eba1f9","start":164,"end":164}}}},"__N_SSG":true}